org.processmining.plugins.interactivevisualization

Interface InteractivityManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LogOverviewVisualizer

    public interface InteractivityManager
    Interface for Interactivity Manager. The Interactivity Manager manages the updates and tags that are communicated between interactive visualizations.
    Author:
    Danny van Heumen

        Parameters:
